        "notes": "Supports computed MemberExpression assignment via JavaScriptRuntime.Object.SetItem(obj, index, value). Works for object literals (ExpandoObject), JavaScriptRuntime.Array index writes (including extending length), and Int32Array index writes. Simple assignments now preserve the spec-required evaluation order by resolving the base reference and computed key before evaluating the right-hand side."
      },
